                </div>
                <h3>RELIABLE SUPPLY</h3>
                <p>Ensuring timely delivery and consistent availability.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="focus__card">
                <div class="focus__icon">
                    <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 3l7 3v6c0 4.6-3 8.4-7 9-4-.6-7-4.4-7-9V6l7-3Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linejoin="round" /><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>QUALITY &amp; TRUST</h3>
